            <p><%= static_snippets.dge?.annotation_note || '' %></p>

            <% if (dge_figures && dge_figures.length > 0) { %>
            <h3>10.1 MA Plot for differentially expressed genes</h3>
            <p><%= static_snippets.dge?.ma_plot_text || '' %></p>

            <h3>10.2 Volcano plot for differentially expressed genes</h3>
            <p><%= static_snippets.dge?.volcano_plot_text || '' %></p>
            <p>Interactive MA and Volcano plots are provided below for each comparison. These plots visualize the distribution of differentially expressed genes and can be expanded for detailed analysis. Click on the expand button (⛶) to view the plot in full screen. The PDF versions of these plots are also available for download.</p>

            <div class="tab-container">
                <% dge_figures.forEach(function(fig, index) { %>
